               <p>HENRY SHEPHERD. I am a <rs id="t18280410-172-viclabel924" type="occupation">journeyman hair-dresser</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-172-victim1000 t18280410-172-viclabel924"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18280410-172-crimeloc925">Kingsland-road</placeName>
