                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-172-off922 t18280410-172-crimeloc925"></join>. I lost a pair of scissors on the 28th of March; I had been using them about ten minutes before; I did not see them taken; I know them by a mark on the bow; I never saw the prisoner in the shop.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280410-172-person1001">
                  EDWARD 
                  OXLEY
               <interp inst="t18280410-172-person1001" type="surname" value="OXLEY"></interp>
